          <img src="../assets/images/factory/qt4-40a-machine-in-production-2.jpg" alt="Mashine ya QT4-40A pamoja na kabati la udhibiti katika karakana" style="width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 1/1; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px;">
